(63, 1, '2015-04-15 16:44:41', '2015-04-15 16:44:41', '<p class="article-h1"><a href="http://software.sil.org/blog/author/davidb/" target="_blank">DAVID </a>| APRIL 10, 2015</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="article-body">\r\n\r\nScripture App Builder 1.0 released the 9th April 2015.\r\n\r\nThe first public release of Scripture App Builder is now available to <a title="Download Scripture App Builder 1.0" href="http://software.sil.org/scriptureappbuilder/download" target="_blank">download</a>.\r\n\r\nThank you to everyone in language teams around the world who have sent feedback, reported bugs and suggested enhancements over the past year. It has truly been an international effort in technical support, development and beta-testing – beginning in Africa and including input from Asia, North and South America, and the Pacific.\r\n\r\nOn the <a href="http://software.sil.org/scriptureappbuilder" target="_blank">new website</a> you can find downloads, documentation, frequently asked questions and links to useful resources. Please let us know how you get on and how your new apps are received.\r\n\r\n[caption id="" align="alignnone" width="200"]<a href="http://software.sil.org/scriptureappbuilder/wp-content/uploads/sites/10/2015/03/SAB-2-200x200px.jpg"><img src="http://software.sil.org/scriptureappbuilder/wp-content/uploads/sites/10/2015/03/SAB-2-200x200px.jpg" alt="" width="200" height="200" /></a> From http://software.sil.org/scriptureappbuilder/[/caption]\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Scripture App Builder 1.0 released!', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'scripture-app-builder-1-0-released', '', '', '2015-04-15 17:50:19', '2015-04-15 17:50:19', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=63', 0, 'page', '', 0),
